        <p>At one point Steven fuses with his human friend Connie to become Stevonnie. Stevonnie is non-binary; one of the writers for the show tweeted that the correct pronouns for Stevonnie are they/them. Not once is Stevonnie mocked for their gender identity, instead they are celebrated. Stevonnie walks into the Donut Shop where Lars and Sadie find themselves with a serious case of the feels for Stevonnie. </p>

      </div>

