        <p>We find no crass discussion on what genitals they could possibly have, a rather disturbing fixation in Western society. There&rsquo;s actually very little focus on gender in Steven Universe which is a refreshing break from the constant stream of gender-binary rhetoric children receive from much of society.</p>

        <div class="quote-right">
